name: The iliaster Dream # Magic Circle 03 #
description:
Magic Circle is a collection based in the order of sacred geometry. Magic Circle is what means "Mandala". Can you keep looking at the center?

This is an interactive piece, move your mouse over the piece to experiment different textures and enjoy the interactrip!

This piece was created based on my studies with Hydra Synth through a  generative code in SVG. 

You can run this directly in hydra through this link >> https://hydra.ojack.xyz/?sketch_id=cLk6mWTGixbPoeUi <<
